rows.label: tev023601_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev023601_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Quince about her work.

rows.label: tev023601_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev023601_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Quince if she's heard any interesting rumors.

rows.label: tev023601_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Quince about her experiences with the Ma-non.

rows.label: tev023601_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Quince about her experiences with the Ma-non.

rows.label: tev023601_SEL0051
rows.name:
Ask Quince about her experiences with
Ma-non technology.

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ummm... So I'm in charge of, like, materials?
You see, the city isn't finished yet, so... Uh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0002
rows.name:
Sorry, I'm terrible at explaining this. People are always
telling me they have no idea what I'm talking about.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0003
rows.name:
Aaaaanyway, we need a whole lot of stuff,
sooo...FrontierNav![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0004
rows.name:
FrontierNav gathers information, and mines Miran
minerals, and...uh...well, it's pretty nifty.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0005
rows.name:
When BLADEs do lots of FrontierNav,
then everyone's happy! Does...that make sense?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0008
rows.name:
When I was working in the administrative district,
I saw a document marked "top secret"![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0009
rows.name:
I thought it would be something cool, like dossiers
on all the men who'd been dumped by Gina.
But it was just something lame. Laaaaame![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0010
rows.name:
...Huh? Gina? Oh, she's a waitress who's always
chatting up the brave boys of BLADE. ...Yeppers.
She's reeeeeall popular with them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0011
rows.name:
...Huh? Oooooh! You wanted to know about the
DOCUMENT![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0012
rows.name:
It was like, blah blah blah, if you destroy certain body
parts of enemies, then they can't use certain Arts that
require those parts, blah blah, whatever. So dull![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0020
rows.name:
Uh-huh... Uh-huuuuh... I see, I see.
So if you use that chip over there...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0021
rows.name:
It's like, I understand Quiquat's frustrations, but I just
don't get things when I read them on a terminal.
I have to get her to explain everything to me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0022
rows.name:
They've really helped us optimize our work, but we
still struggle with communication. I mean, it's not like
I'm just dumb! ...Er, right? I don't think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0039
rows.name:
When we were taking refuge on the Ma-non ship,
Quiquat explained how its power source worked![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0040
rows.name:
Those sparkly wisps of light are living beings that
gather as an energy source to circle around those
thingy-mabobbers on the edges.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0041
rows.name:
...Well? Did that make any sense to you?
It's all just gibberish, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0042
rows.name:
It's not that I'm stupid, right? It's just that Ma-non
technology is THAT advanced! ...Riiiiiight?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0048
rows.name:
I want to get back into my real body!
I want to get back into my real body!
GET! IN! MY! REAL BOOOOOODYYYYYY![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0049
rows.name:
Quiquat was saying they have this incredible technology
that can, like, beam information directly to my BRAIN![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0050
rows.name:
So she's planning to just implant knowledge of their
technology into me! Just like a science-fiction movie![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0051
rows.name:
She'll probably be able to see in my whole brain, huh?
And then, like, if at just that moment there's a freak
power outage, I bet I'll forget everything I knew![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev023601_MSG0052
rows.name:
So when do you think we'll be able to go to the
Lifehold Core? Like...today? Tomorrow? Day after
tomorrow? Week from now? Fortnight?[ST:wait ]
